        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <milestone type="page" n="1"/>
                <head/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline/>
                    <salute>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Gnosiss.</abbr>
                            <expan>Generosissimo</expan>
                        </choice> Viro <choice>
                            <abbr>Dno</abbr>
                            <expan>Domino</expan>
                        </choice> Stanislao Lubieniesio a Lubienietcz <choice>
                            <abbr>
                                <lb/>Is.</abbr>
                            <expan>Ismael</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Bulliald.</abbr>
                            <expan>Bullialdus</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
                            <expan>salutem plurimam dicit</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Epistolam tuam die 29. Decembris scriptam accepi, <del rendition="#s">eique</del>
                    adjunctam <choice>
                        <abbr>Clar. <hi rendition="#sup">mo</hi>
                        </abbr>
                        <expan>Clarissimo</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Dno</abbr>
                        <expan>Domino</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <persName key="Broussel_der_Juengere">Broussello</persName>
                    <add place="superlinear">Senatori Parisiensi</add> reddidi, <subst>
                        <del rendition="#s">a quo</del>
                        <add place="superlinear">cujus</add>
                    </subst> responsum <del rendition="#s">
                        <gap quantity="1" unit="chars"/>
                    </del> simul cum hacce mea accipies. De boni Senis <persName key="ed_axl_wk5_xdb">Riverii</persName> obitu scripsi, qui resignata ac
                    lecta epistola tua, cuncta tibi fausta ac prospera <del rendition="#s">p</del>
                    precatus est.</p>
                <p>Ad tuam aliquot capita ut respondeam, ingenue dicam a Praestantissimo illo Viro,
                    qui <placeName key="Wien">Vienna</placeName> literis datis de statu <placeName key="Deutschland">Germaniae</placeName> scripsit, non ita apposite usurpata
                        <persName key="ed_rby_sbt_b3b">Tiberii</persName> verba, qui Principes
                    mortales, <choice>
                        <abbr>Remp.</abbr>
                        <expan>Rempublicam</expan>
                    </choice> immortalem mortuo <persName key="ed_dwb_pdt_b3b">Germanico</persName>
                    pronunciavit. <del rendition="#s">aptissime</del>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Rom.</abbr>
                        <expan>Romana</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Rep.</abbr>
                        <expan>Republica</expan>
                    </choice> florente, a nullis lacessita formidandis hostibus verum fuit effatum.
                    Hasce vero temporibus Christiani orbis accisis rebus, in praeceps ruente
                        <placeName key="Ungarn">Hungaria</placeName>, legitimo metu attonita ac
                    tantum non nutante <placeName key="Deutschland">Germania</placeName>,
                        turbatissim<del rendition="#ow">ae</del>a <placeName key="Polen">Poloni<del rendition="#ow">ae</del>a </placeName>et viribus valde exhausta,
                    Ingruente <placeName key="Italien">Italiae</placeName>, ob non bene concordantes
                        <rs key="ed_q5k_vhs_52b" type="person">Regis <choice>
                            <abbr>
                                <add place="superlinear">Christianiss.</add>
                            </abbr>
                            <expan>Christianissimi</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </rs> ac <rs key="ed_kpk_yrb_kfb" type="person">
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Sum.</abbr>
                            <expan>Summi</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Pontif.</abbr>
                            <expan>Pontificis</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </rs>animos bello: occult<del rendition="#ow">o</del>is <del rendition="#s">semper</del> odiis ac simultatibus <del rendition="#s">agitati inter </del>
                    <del rendition="#s">se cuncti <choice>
                            <abbr>pnpes</abbr>
                            <expan>principes</expan>
                        </choice> Christiani</del>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Pnpibus</abbr>
                        <expan>Principibus</expan>
                    </choice> Christianis inter se <add place="superlinear">indesinenter</add> certantibus
                    non Tiberii verba sed <subst>
                        <del rendition="#s">alia</del>
                        <add place="superlinear">ista</add>
                    </subst> usurpanda merito mihi videntur, Intercidente <placeName key="ed_mym_zwh_xhb">Imperio</placeName>
                    <add place="superlinear">ac moriente <choice>
                            <abbr>Repub.</abbr>
                            <expan>Republica</expan>
                        </choice> a <rs key="#ed_pfc_31d_kfb" type="place">Turcis</rs>
                        oppressa</add> Caesar occidit: <add place="superlinear">et ad praesentissimum
                        periculum Christiani adducantur.</add> Avertat tantam calamitatem Deus;
                        <milestone type="page" n="2"/>
                        Spiritum concordiae omnibus infundat, cunctorumque collectis viribus <del rendition="#s">vict</del> ac copiis victoriam de hostibus largiatur. Tot
                    capitum, quae <placeName key="Regensburg">Ratisbonae</placeName> simul
                    convenerunt, sensus non bene consentientes, et ad prompte utiliterque <choice>
                        <abbr>Reip.</abbr>
                        <expan>Reipublicae</expan>
                    </choice> consulendum propterea <subst>
                        <del rendition="#s">non bene</del>
                        <add place="superlinear">minus</add>
                    </subst> idoneos, vereor ne <rs key="#ed_pfc_31d_kfb" type="place">Turcae</rs>
                    probe cognitos habeant, ideoque audaci<del rendition="#ow">
                        <gap quantity="2" unit="chars"/>
                    </del>us et consilia Comitiorum, et vires <placeName key="ed_mym_zwh_xhb">Imperii</placeName> spernant, deque pace cogitationes cunctas abiiciant;
                    quamvis <rs key="ed_wpq_n2d_thb" type="person">Sultanum</rs> ad statum
                        <placeName key="Polen">Poloniae</placeName> intuendum observandumque se
                    convertere, ac de pace aut induciis cum <rs key="ed_rzf_5d1_j2b" type="person">Caesare</rs> paciscendis consilia agitare, sint qui suspicentur, idque <add place="superlinear">eis</add> subolet<del rendition="#s"/>.</p>
                <p>
                    <persName key="ed_ohx_ncl_bhb">Michaelem Apaffium</persName> a <rs key="#ed_pfc_31d_kfb" type="place">Turca</rs> Regem <del rendition="#s">appe</del>
                    <placeName key="Ungarn">Hungariae</placeName> appellatum, nec <rs key="#Ungarn" type="place">Hungaris</rs>
                    <rs key="ed_rzf_5d1_j2b" type="person">Caesari</rs> parum fidis hoc displicere<subst>
                        <del rendition="#s">credunt</del>
                        <add place="superlinear">aliqui scribunt</add>
                    </subst>; Mirus technarum artifex <rs key="#ed_pfc_31d_kfb" type="place">Turca</rs>, qui hacce Larva Regia Pannoniis obtrusa, peritissimi aucupis
                    artem exercet: quique cassibus in posterum suis <choice>
                        <abbr>Rege</abbr>
                        <expan>Regem</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>personatu</abbr>
                        <expan>personatum</expan>
                    </choice> et delus<del rendition="#ow">is</del>os stult<del rendition="#ow">is</del>os Hungar<del rendition="#ow">is</del>os interceptos ac illequeatos
                    fractis gulis devorabit.</p>
                <p>Quod ad successorem in regno <placeName key="Polen">Poloniae</placeName> spectat,
                    rege superstite quemquam de illo designando ac eligendo ad Comitia relaturum
                        <del rendition="#s">non</del> facile animum inducere <add place="superlinear">non</add> possum: nec possibile factu; nisi via <choice>
                        <sic>spiritusancti</sic>
                        <corr>spiritus sancti</corr>
                    </choice>, qua Summi aliquando Pontifices renunciati sunt, hoc contigat, puto.
                        <del rendition="#s">
                        <gap quantity="3" unit="chars"/>
                    </del> vicinorum hostium formido ad id forsan Proceres <subst>
                        <del rendition="#s">ad</del>
                        <add place="superlinear">in</add>
                    </subst>ducet, ut interregni             
                    <milestone type="page" n="3"/>
                    incommodis ac periculis <add place="superlinear">quae
                        nunc regno creari queunt</add> obviam eant, et turbas futuras antevertant
                    quicquid erit, <del rendition="#s">lib</del> nisi liberis liberrimae gentis <del rendition="#s">con<gap quantity="3" unit="chars"/>
                    </del> suffragiis, ac consensu quisquam sceptrum <rs key="#Polen" type="place">Polonicum</rs> non adsequetur et obtinebit. Hisce vero temporibus crescente
                        <rs key="#ed_pfc_31d_kfb" type="place">Turcarum Imperio</rs> auct<del rendition="#ow">is</del>aque <pb n="258v"/>potentia, ne electione
                    commendationibus vel minis interturbent <add place="superlinear">
                        <del rendition="#s">nec</del> verendum</add>. <persName key="ed_tzk_21t_b3b">Stephanum Bathoreum</persName> a <rs key="ed_wpq_n2d_thb" type="person">Sultano</rs> commendatum Majores nostri <add place="superlinear">electum</add>
                    viderunt. <del rendition="#s">De <gap quantity="3" unit="chars"/>
                    </del> Caetera, quae de rebus nostris <del rendition="#s">s</del> ad <choice>
                        <abbr>Ill<hi rendition="#sup">m</hi>.</abbr>
                        <expan>Illustrissimum</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Dnm</abbr>
                        <expan>Dominum</expan>
                    </choice>
                    <persName key="Rautenstein">
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Jo.</abbr>
                            <expan>Johannem</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Ern.</abbr>
                            <expan>Ernestum</expan>
                        </choice> de Rautenstein</persName>
                    <add place="superlinear">scribo</add> ex epistola ad ipsum data cognosces; non etenim
                    plura scribere nunc possum.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Vale Vir <choice>
                            <abbr>gnosissime</abbr>
                            <expan>generosissime</expan>
                        </choice> et me ama.</salute>
                    <dateline>
                        <choice>
                            <abbr>Scrib.</abbr>
                            <expan>Scribebam</expan>
                        </choice>
                        <placeName key="Paris">Lutetiae<choice>
                                <abbr>Parisior.</abbr>
                                <expan>Parisiorum</expan>
                            </choice>
                        </placeName>die 25. <del rendition="#s">Febru</del> Januarii 1664. </dateline>
                    <signed/>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
